{"tid":1689660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"玩家撐聰哥 暴雪總裁道歉 示威者拒收貨 BlizzCon踩場","createTime":"2019-11-03T02:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:45:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"845ab54fb63dcb2e8527787f66d7d52f0acba47c","tid":1689660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/DIAYQXQS3LYWQM4ZBCRUHQFDUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2FDIAYQXQS3LYWQM4ZBCRUHQFDUM%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=c3eabfe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2FDIAYQXQS3LYWQM4ZBCRUHQFDUM%2F&h=5862ba67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/DIAYQXQS3LYWQM4ZBCRUHQFDUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n玩家撐聰哥 暴雪總裁道歉<br />\n示威者拒收貨 BlizzCon踩場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國知名遊戲開發商暴雪（Blizzard）在卡牌遊戲《爐石戰記》賽事中，重罰香港電競選手Blitzchung（聰哥），因聰哥曾在賽事中高呼「光復香港，時代革命」，事件引全球遊戲界震怒。逾百玩家昨在暴雪公司的嘉年華會上示威抗議，力撐聰哥。暴雪總裁布拉克（Allen Brack）昨終在暴雪嘉年華（BlizzCon）公開道歉，稱「暴雪沒緊隨自己設下的高標準」，又謂「我們曾有機會團結全世界，但我們沒有做到」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n駐洛杉磯記者張紫茵<br />\n<br />\n昨天是暴雪公司的遊戲發佈會「暴雪嘉年華」，遊戲界翹首以待。不過暴雪早前屈服於中共壓力，重罰香港選手聰哥並取消他的參賽資格、沒收本季獎金及禁賽一年，剝奪其言論自由，觸發不少玩家抵制。昨早在暴雪嘉年華時，網民Dayton Young號召玩家示威，他則專程從俄亥俄州飛到洛杉磯暴雪公司外抗議，現場約有百多名玩家響應，連在NBA玩殘攝影師的12歲男孩Matan亦趕去聲援。<br />\n<br />\n有當地團體自發印製及派發逾4,000件撐港T恤，亦有人選擇穿小熊維尼衣服、戴中共總書記習近平的面具，以示中共打壓言論自由；其中一隻「小熊維尼」更當場向路人派錢，又挑釁的表示「kiss my ass and take my money（巴結我，我就給你錢）」。暴雪總裁布拉克在嘉年華舉辦前，特意出來發表約三分鐘演說，稱「暴雪在月前的電子競技中，曾有機會團結全世界，但我們沒有做到。我們在事件上決策做得太快，結果令事情變得更壞，我們與大家的溝通實在太遲」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/qzf-CAaGTA9Ovdr9B96g2ZWr564=/802x418/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NVIGAEZHP3WIZVFMKPMGBD6OEM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fqzf-CAaGTA9Ovdr9B96g2ZWr564%3D%2F802x418%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNVIGAEZHP3WIZVFMKPMGBD6OEM.gif&h=ec964a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴雪總裁布拉克在會上道歉，但無撤回對聰哥（左圖）的禁賽處分。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ygtfYWtGWxrqsjjgWwa7p_TeZxE=/802x494/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/UTQDY6SYULBRKH3YGKAABONVAY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FygtfYWtGWxrqsjjgWwa7p_TeZxE%3D%2F802x494%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FUTQDY6SYULBRKH3YGKAABONVAY.gif&h=f9fa8ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMatan早前在NBA場館舉撐港T（右圖）而成網紅，昨亦到場聲援。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/9yrY75xmzvwqxnUu7bsGd0cYDDY=/802x494/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/WR2YY52VJN4XGK74XIBATYPTDQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F9yrY75xmzvwqxnUu7bsGd0cYDDY%3D%2F802x494%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FWR2YY52VJN4XGK74XIBATYPTDQ.gif&h=2e22d75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾百位玩家在暴雪嘉年華會上示威抗議，力撐聰哥。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Krb74CWY5FhVMtQAoZrWsjGyJTc=/802x494/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GT4B3HGNXBUM7EKDS4Y6ICRDUM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FKrb74CWY5FhVMtQAoZrWsjGyJTc%3D%2F802x494%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FGT4B3HGNXBUM7EKDS4Y6ICRDUM.gif&h=7e9ecdb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者穿小熊維尼衣服，並戴上習近平的面具示人。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我們沒緊隨自設的高標準」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保時捷播《榮光》警強拖司機落車㩒地押走<br />\n<br />\n布拉克又謂，有兩件事件令其感到最不高興，「第一是我們沒有緊隨自己設下的高標準；第二是我們沒有做到我們當初的目標。為此我在這裏道歉，並接受任何的指摘。」現場爆出一陣歡呼聲及掌聲。布拉克又說：「在我演講之時，外面仍有示威活動，但我們現時渴望透過遊戲再次團結世界，我仍深信遊戲帶來正能量。」他又強調稱「我們之後會做得更好，我更想清楚表明，我們承諾大家能夠用任何方式、任何地方表達自己，我今早已聽到大家的不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n示威者發起人斥欠誠意<br />\n<br />\n對暴雪總裁的道歉，示威發起者Dayton Young並不收貨，他認為暴雪應全面撤回對選手的禁賽處分，並希望暴雪澄清處罰選手的準則。「道歉是正確的，但要有具意義的行動配合，我們沒有聽到暴雪講甚麼，整件事無透明度，他們只是單方面致歉，亦沒有收回對選手的處分。」被禁賽選手之一Casey Chambers也覺得布拉克的道歉誠意不足，指暴雪早前發聲明強調，對聰哥的處分非受中國影響，令他難以置信。"},{"pid":"d4948add47f101ce8b5057371cf58749a418b0f6","tid":1689660,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"聰哥世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f43ad80b0fb169441d6457157ecde49a35e011","tid":1689660,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"中國肯封殺暴雪未"},{"pid":"dc292826e4eb04d7f56f4945660820d6ce284d92","tid":1689660,"uid":242278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"有當地團體自發印製及派發逾4,000件撐港T恤，亦有人選擇穿小熊維尼衣服、戴中共總書記習近平的面具，以示中共打壓言論自由；其中一隻「小熊維尼」更當場向路人派錢，又挑釁的表示<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「kiss my ass and take my money（巴結我，我就給你錢）」</span></span>。暴雪總裁布拉克在嘉年華舉辦前，特意出來發表約三分鐘演說，稱「暴雪在月前的電子競技中，曾有機會團結全世界，但我們沒有做到。我們在事件上決策做得太快，結果令事情變得更壞，我們與大家的溝通實在太遲」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a8330a2dec7aeaa6c10a8e9e431552287cef3","tid":1689660,"uid":157096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"聰哥好嘢，NBA細路好嘢"},{"pid":"49d66756414e30e4338f9aee0af59cf39694e764","tid":1689660,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e291571ad395a9cd7dbb52628ef00e692a837b","tid":1689660,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"8ba2fdb37d9cf5a2d8da0ec27a9eb5af492d311b","tid":1689660,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15f43ad80b0fb169441d6457157ecde49a35e011","tid":1689660,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"中國肯封殺暴雪未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"大把人OW2一出即刻狗衝去買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e43e9e3e52d62c6bcadeb3e19ae024034cb0431","tid":1689660,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3500ff24f49c9985d9ac793a93a4f2a6cb1eff","tid":1689660,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ddc6ef1360fdaeaf5710fdf2b03586a60b3c7d","tid":1689660,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"啲回應十足十林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n避重就輕"},{"pid":"811d37ddfcac068a58b66ef559af25f38accfed4","tid":1689660,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:29:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fb8481a38491862145b5a482ca0ff5b161752c5","tid":1689660,"uid":309176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}